flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: New product launch initiation.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve initial parts order quantities and buffer levels.]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Analyze BOM release schedule and material constraints.]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Remote Functions - Determine optimal buffer levels and mitigation actions.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4{PB: Remote Functions - Plan end-of-life for phased-out components.}
  N4 --> N5[PB: Remote Functions - Execute initial orders and buffer adjustments.]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Exception Management - Monitor and escalate material shortages.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced working capital, protected EBITDA, improved on-time launch delivery.]
  N3 -->|High material constraint risk detected.| B1[Initiate alternative sourcing and expediting actions.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Mitigate EBITDA impact through proactive supply chain actions.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Significant material shortage identif...| B2[Escalate to senior management for expedited recovery.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Ensure timely resolution of critical shortages.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|End-of-life transition risks identified.| B3[Adjust production schedules and inventory levels.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Minimize transition risks and optimize working capital.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]